dc_title_s: Description du pais Normandie; par Damien de Templeux Escuyer Sr. du Frestoy.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes ill. of ships and sea creatures, and uses a special engraving technique to create a wave appearance in the water. The scall cartouche includes the date "1620." From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 32 x 51 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Leclerc, Jean, 1560-1621.,Leclerc, Jean, 1560-1621, cartographer.,Templeux, Damien de, Sieur de Frestoy, engraver.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner, Composite Atlas of France.
